age": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157396929/image_157396929.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745792-undercovered-dozen-lexinfintech-aemetis-hashicorp-cubesmart-plus", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 19:00:29", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745612", "title": "Don't Let Your Savings Melt, Earn 21% Yields Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Harvesting In Agriculture Crop Field.\" data-id=\"1805849861\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ArtistGNDphotography</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-authored by Treading Softly</em></p> <p>Farmers today rarely practice the art of keeping seeds from their current fields to plant in their fields next year. Most farmers sell their entire harvest and buy new seeds from companies that sell in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1805849861/image_1805849861.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745612-dont-let-your-savings-melt-earn-21-percent-yields-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 18:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745310", "title": "Alibaba: Thawing Geopolitical Sentiments May Trigger Rich Recovery Prospects - Maintain Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Global business\" data-id=\"157190899\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PepeLaguarda/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>BABA Is Inherently Undervalued - Offering Opportunistic Investors With A Rich Capital Appreciation Prospect</strong></h2> <p>We previously covered <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4716722-alibaba-restructuring-investment-efforts-appear-promising-bullish-support-growing-baba-stock\">Alibaba Group Holding Limited</a> (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BABA?source=section%253Amain_content%257Cbutton%253Abody_link#hasComeFromMpArticle=false\">BABA</a>) in August 2024, discussing its promising performance metrics in the cloud and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157190899/image_157190899.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745310-alibaba-thawing-geopolitical-sentiments-may-trigger-rich-recovery-prospects-maintain-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 18:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745787", "title": "Grupo Supervielle: Weaker Capital Ratio May Be An Important Constraint For Higher Share Price Returns Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"detail of 100 Argentine peso bills\" data-id=\"1691882118\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Gonzalo Gacitua</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>As I\u2019ve covered in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/labutes-ir\">recent articles</a>, I\u2019m bullish on Argentine banks due to the ongoing economic and social reforms being implemented in the country following Javier Milei\u2019s election victory at the end of 2023, which have boosted Argentine</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1691882118/image_1691882118.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745787-supv-stock-grupo-supervielle-weaker-capital-ratio-constraint-higher-price-returns", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 17:30:44", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745738", "title": "Goldman Sachs BDC: This Is Not A BDC You Want To Have Now", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"girl balancing on red rope with arms outstretched\" data-id=\"2150983341\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In December 2023, I issued my first <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4659842-goldman-sachs-bdc-signs-structural-underperformance-going-forward\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4659842-goldman-sachs-bdc-signs-structural-underperformance-going-forward\" target=\"_blank\">article </a>Goldman Sachs BDC (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GSBD\" title=\"Goldman Sachs BDC\">GSBD</a></span>), plotting a rather bearish thesis. The title of the article captured the essence nicely: <em>Goldman Sachs BDC: Signs Of Structural Underperformance Going Forward</em>. The key message</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150983341/image_2150983341.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745738-goldman-sachs-bdc-this-is-not-a-bdc-you-want-to-have-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 17:15:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4744760", "title": "Very Bad News For REITs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Newspaper Headlines Bad News\" data-id=\"174071285\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1430px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Liliboas</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Before going into this update, please note that I am not trying to be political. There are pros and cons to both parties and their proposed policies, and I am simply analyzing how these policies could affect various REITs. Thank you for</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/174071285/image_174071285.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744760-very-bad-news-for-reits", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 17:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745786", "title": "The Next Big Theme: December 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman holding glowing light bulb with shows light bulb with bank icons outline,finance and banking digital, Finance and banking networks, Digital marketing, cyber security, Business technology.\" data-id=\"1498729115\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"688px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Bussarin Rinchumrus/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>U.S. Infrastructure</h2> <p><em>Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act Funds Flow to More Projects</em></p> <p>On November 15, the third anniversary of the signing of the Infrastructure Investment and Jobs Act, the U.S. Department of Transportation (DOT) announced over $3.4 billion in grants</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1498729115/image_1498729115.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745786-the-next-big-theme-december-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 16:20:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745494", "title": "10 Stocks I'm Buying As REITs Have Never Looked So Good", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Real estate investment trust REIT. Finacial concept 2022\" data-id=\"1370094487\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Funtap</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The market's sharp selloff over the past week puzzled me at first.</p> <p>It seemed to have been triggered by the Fed's changed \"dot plot\" forecast from three rate cuts next year to two. Was that enough to cause such a selloff?</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1370094487/image_1370094487.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745494-10-stocks-im-buying-as-reits-have-never-looked-so-good", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 16:05:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745714", "title": "Weekly Indicators: USD, Commodities, New Orders Face Plant Even As Yield Curve Normalizes", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Piggy banks going over a cliff\" data-id=\"1072593736\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Purpose</h2> <p>I look at the <strong>high frequency weekly indicators</strong> because while they can be very noisy, they provide a good nowcast of the economy, and will telegraph the maintenance or change in the economy well before monthly or quarterly</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593736/image_1072593736.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745714-weekly-indicators-usd-commodities-new-orders-face-plant-even-as-yield-curve-normalizes", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 16:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745782", "title": "Is SolarEdge At Its Final Edge?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"engineering technician Setting up the solar panel inverter in the electrical room Service engineer installs solar cells on factory roofs Concept of clean energy and renewable energy\" data-id=\"2166408868\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2166408868/image_2166408868.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.see